---
/* WCAG 2.2 Checklist:
 * ‚úÖ Proper heading hierarchy
 * ‚úÖ Sufficient color contrast
 * ‚úÖ Images have alt text
 * ‚úÖ Links are descriptive
 * ‚úÖ Timeline is keyboard navigable
